snippet.title: Longplay of The House of the Dead: Overkill - Extended Cut
snippet.description:
Longplay of The House of the Dead: Overkill - Extended Cut, played as the NTSC version on the PlayStation 3. This game's version was released on Oct. 25th, 2011. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!
